lead_paragraph: Australia's in-form scrumhalf Will Genia will replace Nick Phipps against Scotland at Murrayfield on Saturday in coach Mike Cheika's only change to the team that crushed Wales 32-8 in Cardiff last weekend.

headline.print_headline: Australia's Genia to Start at Scrumhalf Against Scotland
